EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
DNC 08, DNC 19.
1. DISTRESS SIGNAL RECEIVED ON 406 MHZ IN
   46-07.70N 024-53.67W AT 031346Z JAN. SEARCH
   AND RESCUE OPERATIONS IN AREA BETWEEN
   47-26.00N 45-15.00N AND 025-23.00W 021-03.00W.

   LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO
   UK COAST GUARD, PHONE: 4423 9255 2100,

2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 25/16.
